snippet.title: World Zero Overhaul Trailer
snippet.description:
The first major update of World Zero is finally here with more to come!
This update was mainly made for bug fixes and reworking the combat but then I ended up getting carried away and added and changed more stuff.

Check out the game here!:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2166170/World_Zero/
